OL,3,C'Serious pollution incident' leaves
OL,4,Cdead fish floating in pond
OL,6,FA "serious pollution incident" in a
OL,7,FPembrokeshire pond has left a "record
OL,8,Fhigh level of ammonia" in the water.
OL,10,FThe Cleddau Project has expressed
OL,11,F"grave concerns" following "visible
OL,12,Fcontamination", and six large dead
OL,13,Ffish were seen floating in Wallis
OL,14,FPond, near Ambleston.
OL,16,FThe community group said concerns were
OL,17,Fraised on Saturday, 9 August.
