OL,3,C'Serious pollution incident' leaves
OL,4,Cdead fish floating in pond
OL,6,FNatural Resources Wales confirmed it
OL,7,Fhas received "reports of possible
OL,8,Fslurry entering a stream that feeds
OL,9,FWallis Pond in".
OL,11,FThe environmental watchdog says an
OL,12,Fenvironment officer visited the pond,
OL,13,Fwhich is a Site of Special Scientific
OL,14,FInterest, on 13 August and "confirmed
OL,15,Fthe presence of three dead fish".
OL,17,FA spokesperson added: "The stream
OL,18,Ffeeding the pond was clear, with no
OL,19,Fsmell or visible signs of pollution.
