OL,3,C'Serious pollution incident' leaves
OL,4,Cdead fish floating in pond
OL,6,F"The pond itself looked murky, but
OL,7,Fthere were no obvious signs of
OL,8,Fcontamination. Live fish were also
OL,9,Fseen in the pond during the visit."
OL,11,FThe community group, which aims to
OL,12,Fprotect wildlife and habitats in
OL,13,FPembrokeshire, criticised Natural
OL,14,FResources Wales for its response.
OL,16,FIt said: "This incident raises grave
OL,17,Fconcerns over NRW's recently revised
OL,18,Fpollution response criteria, which
OL,19,Fmeans they now respond only to reports
OL,20,Fthey deem 'significant'."
